Gabriel Iglesias https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gabriel_Iglesias 0 Gabriel Jesus Iglesias (born July 15, 1976), known comically as Fluffy, is an American comedian, actor, writer, producer and voice actor. He is known for his shows I'm Not Fat… I'm Fluffy and Hot Fluffy.
